"```sql\nSELECT ps.lap\nFROM pitStops ps\nJOIN races r ON ps.raceId = r.raceId\nJOIN drivers d ON ps.driverId = d.driverId\nWHERE r.year = 2011\n  AND r.name = 'Australian Grand Prix'\n  AND d.forename = 'Lewis'\n  AND d.surname = 'Hamilton';\n```\n\nThis SQL query retrieves the lap number during which Lewis Hamilton took a pit stop in the 2011 Australian Grand Prix. It joins the `pitStops`, `races`, and `drivers` tables to filter the results based on the race year, race name, and driver's full name."